OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776420366
OL,3,CTwo police officers charged over crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed pregnant woman
OL,6,FTwo Metropolitan police officers have
OL,7,Fbeen charged over the death of a
OL,8,Fpregnant woman who was killed in a
OL,9,Fcollision with a police vehicle in
OL,10,Fsouth-east London in 2024.
OL,12,FThe woman, 38, died after her vehicle
OL,13,Fwas involved in the crash on Eltham
OL,14,FRoad on October 17 2024. Her unborn
OL,15,Fchild could not be saved.
OL,17,FThe two officers, one of whom is no
OL,18,Flonger with the force, were driving in
OL,19,Fseparate unmarked police cars when the
OL,20,Fcollision took place, the Crown
OL,21,FProsecution Service said.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
