PN,40502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776420366
OL,3,CTwo police officers charged over crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed pregnant woman
OL,6,FPc Chris Johnson, 56, the driver of
OL,7,Fthe police vehicle involved in the
OL,8,Fcollision, has been charged with
OL,9,Fcausing death by dangerous driving.
OL,11,FFormer Pc Danny Tomkins, 35, the
OL,12,Fdriver of the second police vehicle,
OL,13,Fhas been charged with dangerous
OL,14,Fdriving, in relation to the standard
OL,15,Fof his driving.
OL,17,FThey are both due to appear at the
OL,18,FWestminster Magistrates' Court on May
OL,19,F28, the CPS added.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
