OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776420366
OL,3,CTwo police officers charged over crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed pregnant woman
OL,6,FThe force said Johnson is attached to
OL,7,Fthe Met's Taskforce. Tomkins was
OL,8,Fattached to the same unit at the time
OL,9,Fof the incident.
OL,11,FActing Detective Chief Superintendent
OL,12,FJames Derham, who leads policing in
OL,13,FGreenwich, said: "Our thoughts remain
OL,14,Fwith the woman's family and friends,
OL,15,Fwho continue to grieve the loss of her
OL,16,Fand her unborn child. This was a truly
OL,17,Fterrible and heartbreaking incident."
OL,26,@uD@ROUyD@eO]
