PN,40504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776420366
OL,3,CTwo police officers charged over crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed pregnant woman
OL,6,FThe charges follow an investigation by
OL,7,Fthe Independent Office for Police
OL,8,FConduct (IOPC), which began a probe
OL,9,Ffollowing a mandatory referral from
OL,10,Fthe Met.
OL,12,FThe IOPC referred a file to the CPS
OL,13,Ffollowing the conclusion of the
OL,14,Finvestigation in October 2025.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
