OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,406,400,120,260,000,100
PN,40505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1776420366
OL,3,CTwo police officers charged over crash
OL,4,Cwhich killed pregnant woman
OL,6,FMalcolm McHaffie, head of the Crown
OL,7,FProsecution Service's special crime
OL,8,Fdivision, said: "Following a thorough
OL,9,Freview of the evidence in this case,
OL,10,Fwe have authorised criminal charges
OL,11,Fagainst one current and one former
OL,12,Fpolice officer.
OL,14,F"Our prosecutors have worked to
OL,15,Festablish that there is sufficient
OL,16,Fevidence to bring this case to court
OL,17,Fand that it is in the public interest
OL,18,Fto pursue criminal proceedings."
